Package: gts
Type: Package
Title: Gridded time series data manipulation and analysis
Version: 0.2.9017
Author: Ricardo Oliveros-Ramos
Maintainer: Ricardo Oliveros-Ramos <ricardo.oliveros@gmail.com>
Description: Management of gridded time-series (arrays with a time dimension),
    with geographical dimensions (longitude, latitude, depth/altitude). The package provides
    methods to read and write gridded time-series (GTS) objects and manage them using
    R time-series methods. 
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: akima,
         fields,
         lubridate,
         Matrix,
         maps,
         maptools,
         methods,
         mgcv,
         ncdf4,
         nctools,
         sp,
         sf,
         stats
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    reshape2,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://roliveros-ramos.github.io/gts/
BugReports: https://github.com/roliveros-ramos/gts/issues
